title: Cane Creek whips up new eeBrake El Tornado limited edition
content:
There’s no stopping a tornado. But you can stop with a pair of El Tornado eeBrakes from Cane Creek. The latest in their pattern of limited edition colors, like most tornadoes, these won’t be around for long. Since 2017, Cane Creek has been releasing two limited edition eeBrakes every year.
